IDD_dlgSelectCustom DIALOG DISCARDABLE  0, 0, 229, 133
STYLE DS_MODALFRAME | WS_POPUP | WS_CAPTION | WS_SYSMENU
CAPTION "Custom Select Source Dialog"
FONT 8, "MS Sans Serif"
